item.content:encoded:
Do you want to be the most beautiful girl in the world? Do you want to find your own prince charming? Do you want to dress up for banquets and ceremonies? If you like this style, you probably wear a lot of pink and peach colors, dresses, skirts and blouses with cute details, ruffles and lace. If you are a fan of dress-up games, what are you waiting for? Come and experience this game, if you like it, don’t forget to share it with your friends.
Click to play.
